text: "Wild Honey" is a 2000 song by Irish rock group U2. It is the seventh track from their 10th studio album All That You Can't Leave Behind and has a more pop sounding to the album. It was played during the Elevation Tour. It was featured in the 2001 movie Vanilla Sky. ==References== Category:2000 songs Category:Pop songs Category:U2 songs
